%20while%20another%20Microsoft%20staffer%20said%20the%20company%20has%20too%20many%20levels%20and%20layers.%20These%20people%20asked%20not%20to%20be%20identified%20discussing%20sensitive%20matters.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20company%20ended%20up%20with%20many%20layers%2C%20the%20people%20explained%2C%20because%20it%20often%20tried%20to%20reward%20good%20engineers%20by%20promoting%20them%20to%20become%20managers%2C%20sometimes%20with%20as%20few%20as%20one%20or%20two%20reports.%20Often%20those%20engineers-turned-managers%20still%20spent%20most%20of%20their%20time%20in%20the%20codebase%20and%20weren't%20very%20effective%20as%20managers.%20Having%20so%20many%20layers%20of%20management%20also%20proved%20to%20be%20inefficient%2C%20these%20people%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMicrosoft%20doesn't%20have%20any%20centralized%20goals%20for%20span%20of%20control%2C%20or%20number%20of%20reports%20per%20manager%2C%20but%20some%20leaders%20have%20their%20own%20targets%2C%20according%20to%20people%20with%20direct%20knowledge%20of%20the%20situation.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECloud%20%2B%20AI%20boss%20Scott%20Guthrie%2C%20for%20example%2C%20wants%20to%20increase%20the%20span%20of%20control%20in%20his%20organization%20to%20eight%20engineers%20per%20engineering%20manager%2C%20and%20seven%20project%20managers%20per%20manager%2C%20according%20to%20the%20people.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMicrosoft%20Security%20chief%20Charlie%20Bell%20is%20going%20for%20nine%20reports%20per%20manager%2C%20though%20he%20hasn't%20separated%20goals%20for%20span%20of%20control%20of%20engineers%20and%20PMs%2C%20the%20people%20said.%20Bell%20has%2C%20however%2C%20set%20goals%20for%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmicrosoft-mulls-more-job-cuts-managers-non-coders-2025-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eratio%20of%20PMs%20to%20engineers%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20similar%20to%20the%20%26quot%3Bbuilder%20ratio%26quot%3B%20at%20his%20previous%20company%2C%20Amazon%2C%20BI%20previously%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20respon