cement%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20service%20will%20offer%20%26quot%3Blive%20streaming%20and%20on-demand%20access%20to%20the%20full%20portfolio%20of%20FOX%20brands.%26quot%3B%20This%20includes%20FOX%20News%2C%20FOX%20Business%2C%20FOX%20Weather%2C%20FOX%20Sports%2C%20FS1%2C%20FS2%2C%20BTN%20(Big%20Ten%20Network)%2C%20FOX%20Deportes%2C%20and%20local%20FOX%20Stations.%20The%20streamer%20will%20also%20give%20users%20the%20ability%20to%20bundle%20FOX%20Nation%2C%20FOX's%20preexisting%20FOX%20News%20streaming%20service%2C%20under%20one%20platform.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENo%20prices%20or%20details%20on%20plans%20have%20been%20announced%20yet.%20However%2C%20when%20first%20discussing%20the%20streaming%20service%20in%20an%20earnings%20call%20earlier%20this%20year%2C%20Lachlan%20Murdoch%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BOur%20subscriber%20expectation%20will%20be%20modest%2C%20and%20we're%20going%20to%20price%20the%20service%20accordingly%2C%26quot%3B%20per%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffox-launching-new-streaming-service-could-be-a-smart-bet-2025-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider's%20initial%20report%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENBC's%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fstreaming%2Fpeacock-tv-streaming-service-app%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EPeacock%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20CBS's%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fstreaming%2Fparamount-plus-streaming-service%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EParamount%20Plus%3C%2Fa%3E%20are%20two%20relatively%20comparable%20services.%20Both%20streamers%20offer%20plans%20for%20as%20cheap%20as%20%247.99%20a%20month%2C%20but%20users%20need%20to%20upgrade%20for%20%2412.99%20a%20month%20on%20Paramount%20Plus%20and%20%2413.99%20a%20month%20on%20Peacock%20to%20unlock%20CBS%20and%20NBC%20live%20streaming%2C%20respectively.%20These%20higher%20tiers%20also%20include%20other%20perks%2C%20such%20as%20ad-free%20on-demand%20streaming%2C%20downloading%2C%20and%20premiu