%20in%20the%20year%2C%20it%20was%20tested%20in%20the%20Army's%20Expeditionary%20Warrior%20Experiment%202025.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELoitering%20munitions%20are%20becoming%20more%20prolific%20and%20playing%20a%20role%20in%20conflicts%20like%20the%20war%20in%20Ukraine.%20As%20a%20turbojet-powered%20drone%2C%20the%20Hellhound%20is%20unlike%20many%20other%20loitering%20munitions.%20The%20top%20speed%20is%20nearly%20three%20times%20faster%20than%20the%20popular%20Switchblade%20made%20by%20AeroVironment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHellhound%20wrapped%20up%20flight%20tests%20earlier%20this%20year%2C%20and%20the%20S3%20version%20of%20it%2C%20which%20Business%20Insider%20saw%20up%20close%20at%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fus-company-focused-on-rifle-accuracy-now-counter-drone-fight-2025-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3ESOF%20Week%202025%20in%20Tampa%2C%20Florida%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20is%20in%20submission%20for%20the%20US%20Army's%20Low%20Altitude%20Stalking%20and%20Striking%20Ordnance%2C%20or%20LASSO%2C%20program.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELASSO%20requires%20select%20companies%20to%20build%20135%20munitions%20and%2035%20prototypes%20immediately.%20It's%20a%20new-start%20program%2C%20the%20goal%20of%20which%20is%20to%20give%20infantry%20brigades%20better%20stand-off%20weapons%20capabilities.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222016%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20black%20loitering%20munition%20is%20seen%20from%20the%20left-back%20side%20sitting%20on%20a%20white%20table%20in%20an%20office%20space.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68237cbbc6ad288d1480cd00%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221512%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EHellhound%20is%20mostly%203D-printed%20except%20for%20a%20few%20screws%20and%20parts%20that%20are%20off-the-shelf.%3Cp%3ECummings%20Aerospace%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ECummings%20Aerospace's%20CEO%20Sheila%20Cummings%20told%20BI%20that%20much%20of%20how%20her%20company%20is%20thinking%20about%20the%20Hellhound%20has%20been%20with%20modularity%2C%20ease%20of%20manufacturing%2C%20and%20warfighter%20feedback%20in%20mind.%20She%20also%20said%20the%20system%20is%20affordable%20but%20wouldn't%20disclose%20a%20specific%20cost%20or%20price%20range.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20first%20glance%2C%20the%20Hellhound%20loitering%20munition%2C%20sitting%20inside%20its%20case%2C%20looks%20a%20bit%20like%20a%20boogie%20board.%20Weighing%20less%20than%2025%20pounds%2C%20the%20weapon%20is%20fairly%20lightweight%20and%20easy%20to%20pick%20up%20and%20carry.%20There%20are%20straps%20on%20the%20bottom%20that%20can%20attach%20it%20to%20a%20soldier's%20rucksack%2C%20something%20Cummings%20said%20was%20a%20key%20suggestion%20from%20soldiers%20who%20wanted%20the%20system%20to%20be%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffive-critical-capabilities-for-future-war-top-us-lawmaker-2025-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eas%20man-portable%20as%20possible%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20majority%20of%20a%20Hellhound%20is%203D%20printed.%20Cummings%20estimated%20that%2C%20depending%20on%20the%20number%20of%20printers%2C%20they%20could%20fully%20print%20a%20Hellhound%20in%20a%20few%20days%20at%20least%20and%20a%20week%20at%20most.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAny%20part%20that%20isn't%203D-printed%20is%20commercial%20off-the-shelf%2C%20an%20increasingly%20important%20quality%20for%20the%20weapons%20and%20systems%20that%20the%20US%20military%20acquires%20as%20it%20speeds%20up%20the%20process.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20US%20military%20has%20been%20pushing%20for%20more%20of%20its%20systems%2C%20especially%20the%20uncrewed%20weapon%20systems%2C%20to%20be%20suitable%20for%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fus-special-operators-need-more-cheap-weapons-for-next-war-2025-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eproduction%20on%20a%20large%20scale%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20interchangeable%20capabilities%20and%20components%2C%20and%20supply%20chain%20flexibility.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere's%20a%20growing%20realization%20that%20for%20future%20wars%2C%20inexpensive%2C%20easily%20made%20weapons%20will%20be%20needed%20in%20mass%20in%20a%20protracted%2C%20large-scale%20conflict%20against%20a%20major%20rival%20like%20China.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222016%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20black%20loitering%20munition%20sits%20on%20a%20white%20table%20in%20an%20office%20space.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68236e69c6ad288d1480c9f3%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221512%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ECummings%20said%20feedback%20from%20soldiers%20helped%20Cummings%20Aerospace%20add%20straps%20to%20the%20Hellhound's%20case%20so%20that%20it%20could%20attach%20to%20a%20rucksack.%3Cp%3ECummings%20Aerospace%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EA%20key%20development%20of%20the%20Ukraine%20war%20has%20been%20how%20Ukraine%20has%20created%20an%20arsenal%20of%20cheap%20drones%20for%20surveillance%20and%20precision%20strike.%20That's%20something%20militaries%20around%20the%20world%20are%20watching%20closely%20given%20how%20effective%20it's%20been.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe're%20really%20trying%20to%20minimize%20the%20exquisite%2C%20custom%20products%2C%26quot%3B%20Cummings%20told%20BI%2C%20explaining%20that%20the%20Hellhound's%20payload%2C%20too%2C%20can%20be%20interchanged%20with%20different%20sensors%20or%20warheads%20depending%20on%20what%20the%20mission%20requirements%20are%20simply%20by%20twisting%20and%20unlocking%20the%20nose.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20defining%20characteristic%20of%20the%20Hellhound%20is%20its%20turbojet%20engine.%20Cummings%20said%20it's%20a%20differentiator%20for%20the%20system%20and%20company%20as%20it%20not%20only%20reduces%20fuel%20usage%20but%20also%20increases%20speed.%20Cummings%20Aerospace%20advertises%20the%20Hellhound%20as%20being%20able%20to%20fly%20faster%20than%20375%20mph%20with%20a%20range%20of%20around%2025%20miles.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20turbojet%20engine%20is%20also%20a%20c