20to-do%20list.%20%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20a%20turning%20point%20%E2%80%94%20that%20moment%20of%20surrender%20%E2%80%94%20that%20helped%20lighten%20her%20mental%20load.%20She%20began%20to%20focus%20on%20what%20truly%20needed%20her%20attention%3A%20her%20baby.%20And%20perhaps%2C%20slowly%2C%20herself.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%E2%80%9CI%20was%20so%20sleep%20deprived%20that%20all%20I%20just%20told%20myself%20was%20that%20I%20need%20to%20just%20keep%20the%20baby%20alive%20and%20healthy%2C%20everything%20else%20is%20secondary.%20As%20I%20found%20ways%20to%20ensure%20I%20got%20some%20good%20sleep%2C%20I%20gradually%20began%20to%20focus%20on%20the%20baby%20and%20only%20do%20that%2C%20while%20my%20husband%20took%20care%20of%20my%20recovery.%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHer%20honesty%20is%20striking%20%E2%80%94%20something%20every%20new%20mom%20can%20likely%20relate%20to.%20The%20late-night%20Google%20searches%2C%20the%20endless%20advice%2C%20the%20contradictory%20dos%20and%20don%E2%80%99ts%20%E2%80%94%20all%20of%20it%20adds%20to%20the%20noise.%20And%20Priyanka%E2%80%99s%20been%20there%20too.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9C%3Cem%3EWhen%20in%20doubt%2C%3C%2Fem%3E%20the%20first%20thing%20new%20mothers%20do%2C%20including%20me%2C%20is%20to%20browse.%20That%20itself%20gives%20a%20lot%20of%20stress.%20The%20research%20we%20do%20gives%20us%20a%20lot%20of%20information%2C%3Cem%3E%20which%20is%2C%20mostly%20contradicting%20what%20the%20doctor%20says.%20When%20we%20stop%20doing%20this%2C%20I%20think%20a%20lot%20of%20our%20mental%20load%20is%20off%20our%20heads%2C%20and%20new%20mothers%20can%20think%20clearly.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20Priyanka%2C%20the%20early%20days%20of%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F111340%2Fmothering-is-in-the-love-not-in-the-blood%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emotherhood%3C%2Fa%3E%20felt%20less%20like%20an%20emotional%20whirlwind%20and%20more%20like%20checking%20things%20off%20a%20to-do%20list.%20It%20became%20a%20job%20%E2%80%94%20one%20she%20threw%20herself%20into%2C%20completely.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9C%3Cem%3EWhile%20taking%20care%20of%20my%20baby%2C%20I%20didn%E2%80%99t%20bring%20in%20emotions%2C%20and%20I%20had%20a%20to-do%20list%20in%20my%20mind%20and%20struck%20off%20things%20as%20I%20finished%20them.%20I%20never%20thought%20about%20myself.%20It%20was%20always%20the%20baby.%20I%20think%20mothers%20just%20power%20through%20everything%2C%20small%20or%20big%20challenges%2C%20after%20they%20give%20birth%20to%20their%20baby.%20The%20secret%20is%20to%20just%20go%20with%20the%20flow%20and%20not%20think%20much%2C%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%9D%20she%20says%20with%20raw%20honesty.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20make%20daily%20life%20a%20little%20more%20manageable%2C%20they%20decided%20to%20bring%20in%20help.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9C%3Cem%3ESo%20as%20to%20ease%20the%20daily%20duties%20as%20a%20mother%2C%20we%20hired%20a%20help%2C%20to%20bathe%20and%20massage%20the%20baby%2C%20wash%20her%20clothes%20and%20more.%20For%20other%20tasks%20of%20playing%20with%20her%20or%20reading%20her%20a%20book%20we%20have%20my%20parents%20and%20in-laws%20around%2C%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%9D%20she%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20for%20routines%2C%20Priyanka%20has%20let%20go%20of%20the%20idea%20of%20a%20strict%20schedule%20%E2%80%94%20something%20she%20once%20held%20close.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9C%3Cem%3EI%20just%20know%20what%20I%20have%20to%20finish%20during%20the%20day.%20There%20is%20no%20timing%20set%20for%20any%20of%20the%20tasks.%20I%20was%20someone%20who%20had%20a%20schedule%20for%20everything%20but%20now%20I%20have%20come%20to%20terms%20with%20not%20having%20a%20schedule%20and%20that%20it%20is%20all%20about%20the%20baby%E2%80%99s%20demands.%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20just%20three%20months%2C%20this%20new%20mother%20has%20learned%20one%20of%20the%20most%20important%20lessons%20of%20all%20%E2%80%94%20that%20motherhood%20rarely%20goes%20by%20the%20book.%20And%20sometimes%2C%20the%20best%20way%20to%20show%20up%20is%20simply%20to%20flow%20with%20the%20chaos.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EEarly%20to%20rise%2C%20last%20to%20sleep%3A%20how%20mothers%20made%20it%20work%2040%20years%20ago%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENo%20smartphones%20to%20set%20reminders.%3Cbr%3ENo%20appliances%20to%20make%20cooking%20easier.%3Cbr%3ENo%20washing%20machines%20to%20lighten%20the%20load.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThat%E2%80%99s%20what%20daily%20life%20looked%20like%20for%20Sai%20Chitra%20Venkatesh%20and%20Bhavani%20Krishnamurthy%20when%20they%20became%20new%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F99660%2Fincredible-mother-nurtures-33-children-tulsi-parihar%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emothers%20in%20the%201980s%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMarried%20into%20the%20same%20home%2C%20Bhavani%20(65)%20and%20Chitra%20(55)%20say%20living%20in%20a%20joint%20family%20made%20everything%20manageable%20%E2%80%94%20even%20joyful.%20It%20gave%20them%20the%20support%2C%20reassurance%2C%20and%20shared%20strength%20that%20every%20new%20mother%20needs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20co-sisters%20settled%20in%20for%20a%20nostalgic%20chat%20with%20us%2C%20taking%20a%20warm%2C%20honest%20walk%20down%20memory%20lane%20%E2%80%94%20back%20to%20the%20days%20when%20motherhood%20looked%20very%20different%2C%20yet%20felt%20just%20as%20consuming.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CMy%20daughter%20was%20born%20in%201985%2C%20and%20I%20was%2026.%20While%20my%20husband%20had%20just%20launched%20his%20business%2C%20I%20relied%20heavily%20on%20my%20mother-in-law%2C%20brother-in-law%2C%20and%20Chitra%20with%20the%20baby%E2%80%99s%20work.%20And%20today%20I%20can%20tell%20it%20was%20the%20three%20of%20them%20who%20raised%20my%20daughter%20while%20I%20took%20care%20of%20the%20home%2C%20made%20meals%20for%20all%2C%20and%20d