ther-in-law%20cared%20for%20the%20little%20ones.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CBeing%20in%20a%20joint%20family%20can%20be%20a%20big%20blessing%2C%20provided%20one%20overlooks%20all%20the%20differences%20in%20opinion.%20Any%20task%20or%20challenge%20was%20made%20simpler%20and%20dealt%20with%20easily%20because%20there%20were%20so%20many%20to%20help%20around%2C%20especially%20when%20it%20came%20to%20any%20issues%20with%20the%20baby%2C%E2%80%9D%20Chitra%20explains.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBack%20in%20the%2080s%2C%20the%20roles%20in%20most%20households%20were%20sharply%20divided%20%E2%80%94%20men%20earned%20the%20money%2C%20and%20women%20took%20care%20of%20everything%20else.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhile%20they%20brought%20in%20the%20money%2C%20we%20provided%20all%20the%20care%20the%20kids%20and%20others%20needed.%20So%20our%20goals%20and%20aims%20were%20very%20clear%20and%20as%20a%20team%20we%20worked%20towards%20that%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20ladies%20share.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThey%20admit%20they%20didn%E2%80%99t%20know%20words%20like%20%3Cem%3Epostpartum%20depression%3C%2Fem%3E%20or%20%3Cem%3Ebaby%20blues%3C%2Fem%3E.%20They%20didn%E2%80%99t%20have%20terms%20for%20the%20hormonal%20upheavals%20or%20mental%20load%2C%20but%20that%20didn%E2%80%99t%20mean%20the%20emotions%20weren%E2%80%99t%20real.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CHence%2C%20we%20didn%E2%80%99t%20pay%20attention%20to%20any%20of%20those.%20We%20only%20lived%20every%20day%20for%20the%20love%20we%20had%20for%20our%20children%2C%20and%20that%20gave%20us%20so%20much%20clarity%20on%20the%20tasks%20we%20had%20to%20carry%20out%20for%20them%2C%E2%80%9D%20shares%20Chitra.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEach%20day%20was%20full%20to%20the%20brim%20%E2%80%94%20waking%20up%20before%20everyone%20else%2C%20sleeping%20after%20the%20whole%20household%20had%20turned%20in.%20There%20were%20no%20shortcuts%2C%20just%20relentless%20energy%20and%20deep%20love.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThis%20is%20how%20a%20day%20looked%20for%20us%2030%20years%20ag